205
00:16:49,978 --> 00:16:52,018
Tidak, katakan padaku.

206
00:16:53,449 --> 00:16:54,919
Kau tidak bisa pulang sebelum memberi tahuku.

207
00:16:57,059 --> 00:16:59,959
