00:20:03,738 --> 00:20:04,778
Ini.

236
00:20:11,349 --> 00:20:12,719
Aku lupa caranya.

237
00:20:13,318 --> 00:20:14,449
Bukankah ini?

238
00:20:25,869 --> 00:20:27,199
